  description: You have made it to the grandest stage of them all. The temple of
    Harux is the place where all the finals of the intergalactic championships have
    been held. Before that, the finals of the ArrowHex planetary tournaments on Kaaman
    have been held at the same temple. For almost 50,000 years this temple has seen
    countless games of ArrowHex and this is where you can write your name in the
    history books. Get ready for the most glorious game of your life and become the
    Intergalactic Champion.
